/Nh%E1%BA%ADt-m%E1%BB%99-Th%C3%A1i-giang-h%C3%A0nh-chu/poem-LcvW9SrHzYcNokJGjVwzQQ">Nhật mộ Thái giang hành chu - 日暮泰江行舟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/Th%E1%BB%8B-y%E1%BA%BFn/poem-z7guycCGz02MA5Ik49qVkg">Thị yến - 侍宴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/author-eVhiQaGgvOZuXB8qH633Iw">Thẩm Thuyên Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Cao/T%E1%BB%B1-ph%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-5pG21Opvfb66SZjM6ZPeLQ">Tự phận ca - 自分歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Cao/author-C1VQ72lNTKL4OeInJcXgDw">Nguyễn Cao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%87t/Xu%C3%A2n-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-RXj46PWN7ayU3_GzK12rmA">Xuân biệt - 春別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%87t/author-BtKd6zfpocHUK3K04X_bBQ">Chương Kiệt</a>)<br></div>	</div>
